WEBVTT

00:01:28.705 --> 00:01:31.927
Sex workers sometimes
have two degrees, a bank job

00:01:31.951 --> 00:01:33.759
and a prominent role in church.

00:01:33.783 --> 00:01:34.787
(Laughter)

00:01:34.811 --> 00:01:35.973
On any given day,

00:01:35.997 --> 00:01:39.326
there can be either a party
or a burned body

00:01:39.350 --> 00:01:40.745
in the middle of a street.

00:01:42.724 --> 00:01:45.505
There is so much that is possible in Lagos

00:01:45.529 --> 00:01:46.719
and so much that isn't,

00:01:46.743 --> 00:01:49.956
and very often the difference
between possibility and impossibility

00:01:49.980 --> 00:01:51.594
is simply who you are,

00:01:51.618 --> 00:01:54.137
and if you're lucky enough,
who you're connected to.

00:01:54.852 --> 00:01:57.041
Belonging in Lagos is a fluid concept

00:01:57.065 --> 00:02:01.193
determined by ethnic origin,
sexual orientation, gender,